Mbongoro (donkey in English) imhuka inopfuyiwa pamusha inosandiswa kuita mabasa ekuzvuva ringava gejo kana kuti ngoro. MuZimbabwe mbongoro haidyiwe, asi kunyika dzinoti Namibia neBotswana kunonzi kune marudzi anodya mbongoro.

